ing scheme. The exact\nadvantage is quantified for a problem of sampling and reconstructing an audio\nfield.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Nov 2012 10:05:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-12"}
