erator (lattice Bhatnagar-Gross-Krook vs.\\ multiple\nrelaxation time) and velocity set (D3Q15 vs.\\ D3Q19 vs.\\ D3Q27) does not\nsignificantly affect the accuracy in the problems studied.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 1 Nov 2012 15:32:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 13 Aug 2013 10:33:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-02-21"}
